~ Tasks (functions) in Sprout.
~ A task can take inputs and 'give' back a result.

task greet(person):
    show "Hello, " + person + "!"
    give upper(person)

task add(a, b):
    give a + b

~ Tasks can even call themselves (recursion).
task factorial(n):
    when n <= 1:
        give 1
    give n * factorial(n - 1)

make loud = greet("world")
show "greet gave back:", loud

show "2 + 3 =", add(2, 3)
show "factorial(5) =", factorial(5)
